Link to original:  SCP-ES-100

Note from the translators:



Our final work of the showcase is here. SCP-ES-100's inspiration was a horror story that the author heard from his brother. The author wanted to pay homage to Series 1-3, starting with an apparently simple anomaly, next he offers background and development seen in Series 2 and finally in the final addendum it shows a complex SCP seen in Series 3. All of that with a good aesthetic and code to make it more Foundation-like.

Hope that you enjoy this work. It’s the best one from this author and the fourth highest rated in the Spanish Branch, all in 1 year.
